URL: https://github.com/hydroepix/hydroepixr
BugReports: https://github.com/hydroepix/hydroepixr/issues
Description: The primary purpose of Hydroepix (HE) is to model the spread of 
    fish pathogens in marine sites. We use the example of the introduction and 
    waterborne spread of infectious salmon anaemia virus infection (ISAV) into an 
    Atlantic salmon site; however, model scripts can be adapted to other diseases 
    and to other fish species.
